---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Technik Elektryk - ZSEiU Łaziska Górne" description="Technik elektryk w ZSEiU Łaziska Górne – programowanie sterowników PLC, instalacje elektryczne, systemy Smart Home, odnawialne źródła energii (OZE) i uprawnienia SEP.">

  <article class="w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto min-w-0">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-linear-to-br from-slate-900 via-amber-950 to-slate-900 dark:from-navy-950 dark:via-amber-950/70 dark:to-navy-950 border border-slate-700/50 dark:border-amber-900/30 p-5 sm:p-10 mb-10 w-full">
      <div class="electric-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="electric-glow absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-80 h-80 bg-amber-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="electric-glow absolute -bottom-20 -left-20 w-80 h-80 bg-orange-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-300 border border-amber-500/30 mb-4">Technikum w ZSEiU</span>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3 leading-tight wrap-break-word">Technik <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-amber-300 via-yellow-400 to-orange-400">Elektryk</span></h1>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed wrap-break-word">Zasilamy przyszłość – nowoczesne instalacje elektryczne, automatyka Smart Home, sterowanie PLC i odnawialne źródła energii.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- STATYSTYKI -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 sm:gap-4 my-10 w-full">
      <div class="stat-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-5 text-center min-w-0" data-count-to="5">
        <span class="block text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400"><span class="stat-value">0</span> lat</span>
        <span class="block mt-1 text-xs sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-snug">nauki w technikum</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-5 text-center min-w-0" data-count-to="2">
        <span class="block text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400"><span class="stat-value">0</span></span>
        <span class="block mt-1 text-xs sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-snug">kwalifikacje zawodowe</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-5 text-center min-w-0" data-count-to="70">
        <span class="block text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400"><span class="stat-value">0</span>+ lat</span>
        <span class="block mt-1 text-xs sm:text-base text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-snug">tradycji szkoły</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TECHNOLOGIE -->
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-10 mb-6 pl-3 sm:pl-4 border-l-4 border-amber-500 leading-snug wrap-break-word">Technologie i obszary kształcenia</h2>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6 wrap-break-word">
      Kształcimy fachowców w oparciu o standardy nowoczesnej gospodarki sieciowej i elektroenergetycznej, z naciskiem na automatyzację i zieloną energię.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 xs:grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-3 mb-8 w-full">
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Smart Home</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"></rect><path d="M6 10h12M6 14h12"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Sterowniki PLC</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><path d="M12 2v2M12 20v2M4.93 4.93l1.41 1.41M17.66 17.66l1.41 1.41M2 12h2M20 12h2M6.34 17.66l-1.41 1.41M19.07 4.93l-1.41 1.41"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"></circle></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">OZE / Solar</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"></polygon></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Uprawnienia SEP</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Utrzymanie ruchu</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Ochrona p-poraż.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tech-chip rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-3 sm:p-4 text-center min-w-0 hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-navy-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 shrink-0">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"></line></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="block text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Systemy CAD</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CZEGO SIĘ NAUCZYSZ -->
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-10 mb-6 pl-3 sm:pl-4 border-l-4 border-amber-500 leading-snug wrap-break-word">Czego nauczysz się podczas nauki?</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8 w-full">
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"></path></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Projektowanie i montaż instalacji</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>instalacje mieszkaniowe, przemysłowe i oświetleniowe</li>
              <li>wykonywanie instalacji alarmowych i domofonowych</li>
              <li>czytanie i tworzenie profesjonalnych schematów elektrycznych (CAD)</li>
              <li>dobieranie zabezpieczeń, przewodów i aparatury</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Maszyny i urządzenia elektryczne</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>budowa i diagnostyka silników oraz prądnic</li>
              <li>podłączanie układów rozruchowych i regulacyjnych</li>
              <li>konserwacja, naprawa i przeglądy maszyn elektrycznych</li>
              <li>praca z transformatorami i rozdzielnicami</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"></rect><path d="M6 10h12M6 14h12"></path></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Automatyka i sterowniki PLC</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>nauka programowania przemysłowych sterowników logicznych (PLC)</li>
              <li>tworzenie algorytmów sterowania procesami</li>
              <li>projektowanie i montaż szaf sterowniczych</li>
              <li>obsługa układów pneumatyki i sensoryki</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><path d="M12 2v2M12 20v2M4.93 4.93l1.41 1.41M17.66 17.66l1.41 1.41M2 12h2M20 12h2M6.34 17.66l-1.41 1.41M19.07 4.93l-1.41 1.41"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"></circle></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Odnawialne Źródła Energii (OZE)</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>montaż i uruchamianie instalacji fotowoltaicznych</li>
              <li>konfigurowanie falowników i magazynów energii</li>
              <li>zasada działania pomp ciepła i kolektorów</li>
              <li>optymalizacja zużycia energii w budynkach</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"></line><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"></line><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"></line></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Pomiary i diagnostyka</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>posługiwanie się miernikami wielofunkcyjnymi i oscyloskopem</li>
              <li>badanie stanu izolacji i rezystancji uziemień</li>
              <li>lokalizowanie i usuwanie uszkodzeń w obwodach elektrycznych</li>
              <li>tworzenie protokołów z pomiarów instalacji</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-navy-800/70 border border-slate-200 dark:border-navy-700 p-4 sm:p-5 hover:shadow-md hover:border-amber-400 dark:hover:border-amber-600 transition-all duration-300 min-w-0">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white wrap-break-word">Bezpieczeństwo i pierwsza pomoc</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 list-disc list-inside">
              <li>dobieranie i sprawdzanie ochrony przeciwporażeniowej</li>
              <li>bezpieczne wykonywanie prac pod napięciem (BHP)</li>
              <li>postępowanie w stanach zagrożenia życia i porażenia prądem</li>
              <li>pierwsza pomoc przedmedyczna</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TIMELINE 5 LAT -->
    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-10 mb-6 pl-3 sm:pl-4 border-l-4 border-amber-500 leading-snug wrap-break-word">Jak wygląda nauka przez 5 lat?</h2>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6 wrap-break-word">
      Program technikum łączy przedmioty ogólne, zawodowe oraz praktyczną naukę w laboratoriach szkolnych i zakładach pracy. Uczniowie przygotowują się do dwóch kluczowych egzaminów zawodowych.
    </p>

    <div class="relative mb-8 w-full">
      <div class="hidden sm:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-navy-700 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-4 sm:gap-8">
          <div class="hidden sm:flex sm:w-1/2 justify-end">
            <div class="text-right">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-navy-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold text-sm mb-1">I</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Podstawy elektrotechniki i BHP</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Rysunek techniczny, prawa prądu, pomiary podstawowe</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden sm:flex shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-500 items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-navy-900 z-10">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs">1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2">
            <div class="sm:hidden flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
              <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center ring-2 ring-white dark:ring-navy-900"><span class="text-white font-bold text-xs">1</span></span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white min-w-0 flex-1 wrap-break-word">Klasa I – Podstawy elektrotechniki i BHP</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 sm:hidden">Rysunek techniczny, prawa prądu, pomiary podstawowe</p>
            <p class="hidden sm:block text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-1">Poznajesz podstawowe pojęcia, schematy i zasady bezpieczeństwa pracy z energią elektryczną. Uczysz się badać proste obwody w laboratoriach.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row-reverse items-start gap-4 sm:gap-8">
          <div class="hidden sm:flex sm:w-1/2">
            <div>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-navy-700 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-bold text-sm mb-1">II</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Montaż maszyn i instalacji</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Budowa silników, montaż okablowania, trasowanie</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden sm:flex shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-500 items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-navy-900 z-10">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs">2</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:text-right">
            <div class="sm:hidden flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
